queryResponse.sql:
-- use existing users in LOOKER_SCRATCH.LR$YVJ111678061096044_users
-- use existing shipment_price_request_matches in LOOKER_SCRATCH.LR$YVMY71678135321801_shipment_price_request_matches
SELECT
    shipper_applications.name  AS "shipper_applications.name",
    COUNT(DISTINCT CASE WHEN (CASE WHEN shipments.is_tonu  THEN 1 ELSE 0 END
) = 0 THEN shipments.id  ELSE NULL END) AS "shipments.shipment_count",
    COUNT(DISTINCT CASE WHEN (price_requests_last.source in ('shipper_api','transfix_rates_api','transfix_tms','email_quoting_tool', 'shipper_watched_lanes', 'shipper_generated_price','real_time_rating')) AND (((CASE
WHEN shipments.shipper_rate_type = 'contract_backup'  THEN 'Backup/Published'
WHEN shipments.shipper_rate_type = 'contract_primary' or shipments.priced_under_contract = 'true' THEN 'Contract'
WHEN coalesce(shipments.shipper_rate_type = 'spot', true)  THEN 'Spot'

END) = 'Spot')) THEN shipments.id  ELSE NULL END) AS "shipments.shipment_spot_auto_bid_count",
    COUNT(DISTINCT CASE WHEN (accepted_bid.accepted_by_id is not null and accepted_bid.carrier_application_id=shipments.carrier_application_id and (accepted_bid.declined_by_id is null)) and ((trim(accepted_bid.source)) not in ('manual','covered','offered')) and accepted_bid.id is not null  THEN shipments.id  ELSE NULL END) AS "shipments.shipment_auto_booked_count",
    COUNT(DISTINCT CASE WHEN NOT (CASE
WHEN shipments.source in ('edi-worker', 'grandmaster', 'edi-mapper')  THEN 'EDI'
WHEN (shipments.source in ('stark') and (created_by.email like '%transfix.io%') = false)  THEN 'Terminal'
WHEN shipments.source in ('stark')  THEN 'Manual'
WHEN shipments.source in ('tms', 'TMS')  THEN 'TMS'
WHEN shipments.source in ('email')  THEN 'Email'
WHEN shipments.source in ('justransform')  THEN 'Just Transform'
WHEN true  THEN 'Other'

END) in ('Manual')  THEN shipments.id  ELSE NULL END) AS "shipments.shipment_auto_built_count",
    COUNT(DISTINCT CASE WHEN (((CASE
WHEN shipments.shipper_rate_type = 'contract_backup'  THEN 'Backup/Published'
WHEN shipments.shipper_rate_type = 'contract_primary' or shipments.priced_under_contract = 'true' THEN 'Contract'
WHEN coalesce(shipments.shipper_rate_type = 'spot', true)  THEN 'Spot'

END) = 'Backup/Published')) AND ((CASE WHEN shipments.is_tonu  THEN 1 ELSE 0 END
) = 0) THEN shipments.id  ELSE NULL END) AS "shipments.shipment_backup_count"
FROM stark_prod.recreated_tables.shipments  AS shipments
LEFT JOIN LOOKER_SCRATCH.LR$YVMY71678135321801_shipment_price_request_matches AS shipment_price_request_matches ON (shipment_price_request_matches."SHIPMENT_ID")=shipments.id
LEFT JOIN stark_prod.recreated_tables.custom_trunc_price_requests  AS price_requests_last ON price_requests_last.price_request_id = (shipment_price_request_matches."PRICE_REQUEST_ID")
INNER JOIN stark_prod.recreated_tables.shipper_applications  AS shipper_applications ON shipper_applications.id = shipments.shipper_application_id
LEFT JOIN stark_prod.recreated_tables.bids  AS accepted_bid ON shipments.id=accepted_bid.shipment_id
              and shipments.carrier_application_id=accepted_bid.carrier_application_id
              and (accepted_bid.accepted_by_id is not null and accepted_bid.carrier_application_id=shipments.carrier_application_id and (accepted_bid.declined_by_id is null))
              and (TO_CHAR(TO_DATE(CONVERT_TIMEZONE('UTC', 'America/New_York', CAST(accepted_bid.declined_at  AS TIMESTAMP_NTZ))), 'YYYY-MM-DD')) is null
LEFT JOIN LOOKER_SCRATCH.LR$YVJ111678061096044_users AS created_by ON created_by.id=shipments.created_by_id
WHERE ((( shipments.dispatched_at  ) >= ((CONVERT_TIMEZONE('America/New_York', 'UTC', CAST(DATEADD('month', -2, DATE_TRUNC('month', DATE_TRUNC('day', CONVERT_TIMEZONE('UTC', 'America/New_York', CAST(CURRENT_TIMESTAMP() AS TIMESTAMP_NTZ))))) AS TIMESTAMP_NTZ)))) AND ( shipments.dispatched_at  ) < ((CONVERT_TIMEZONE('America/New_York', 'UTC', CAST(DATEADD('month', 3, DATEADD('month', -2, DATE_TRUNC('month', DATE_TRUNC('day', CONVERT_TIMEZONE('UTC', 'America/New_York', CAST(CURRENT_TIMESTAMP() AS TIMESTAMP_NTZ)))))) AS TIMESTAMP_NTZ))))))
GROUP BY
    1
ORDER BY
    2 DESC
FETCH NEXT 500 ROWS ONLY
